high_descs: Walk to the sink on your left.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the potato and then pick the potato up from the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the black trash can next to the counter.
Place the potato in the black trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato into the black trash can.

high_descs: Move forward and face the kitchen sink on your left.
Pick up the potato that is in the sink.
Turn around to face the microwave that is above the stove behind you.
Place the potato between the two cups in the microwave and heat it before pulling it back out.
Turn left, walk until you reach the end of the kitchen island, then hang a left to face the trash bin.
Place the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato into a trash bin.

high_descs: Walk forward and then turn left at the sink
Pick up a potato from in the sink
Turn to your left and then turn around to face the microwave
Cook the potato in the microwave for a few seconds and then pick it back up
Turn to your left, walk past the kitchen counter and then turn to face the trash can
Throw the potato in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Microwave a potato and throw it away
